        "conditionKey": "a5SweetSlumberUndisturbed",
        "source": "Layla",
        "description": "A5 Sweet Slumber Undisturbed: DMG dealt by the Shooting Stars fired by Nights of Formal Focus (Elemental Skill) is increased by 1.5% of Layla's Max HP. No confirmed eval-time HP-to-DMG conversion key exists, so this is approximated as a flat DMG add at an assumed 30,000 Max HP (a representative HP-invested Layla build): 0.015 x 30000 = 450. Applied via skill_dmgInc, which also slightly over-buffs the initial Nights of Formal Focus cast hit (skillDmg) since no bespoke bonus key isolates starDmg. Admin can override via the LB builder UI for a different HP assumption.",
